Right. And it doesn't overload &quot;class&quot; with possibly-changeable semantics. So for BOTH reasons, I think i'd like to specifically propose that this idea get re-examined!<br /><br />To specifically restate: I propose that WHAT-WG move the &quot;predefined classes&quot; idea into its OWN attribute. &quot;role&quot; is one possible name for the new attribute; I'm sure others can be thought of.<br /><br />Adrienne L. Travis<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.whatwg.org/bb3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=62">adrienne</a> — Wed Apr 25, 2007 3:35 pm</p><hr />
